"use strict";(self.webpackChunkdecomp_www=self.webpackChunkdecomp_www||[]).push([[477],{10:e=>{e.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"updates","metadata":{"permalink":"/blog/updates","source":"@site/blog/2025-01-20-test.md","title":"January 2025","description":"Current Development Status","date":"2025-01-20T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"January 20, 2025","tags":[{"label":"updates","permalink":"/blog/tags/updates"}],"readingTime":1.745,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"Fimmel","title":"Admin","url":"https://github.com/F1mmel","email":"contact@fimmel.dev","socials":{"github":"F1mmel"},"imageURL":"https://github.com/F1mmel.png","key":"Fimmel"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"updates","title":"January 2025","authors":"Fimmel","tags":["updates"]}},"content":"## **Current Development Status**\\r\\nWe are excited to share the progress of our fan project! Below is a detailed log of updates, new features, and planned improvements.\\r\\n\\r\\n---\\r\\n\\r\\n## **Changelog**\\r\\n\\r\\n### **January 2025**\\r\\n- **Graphics & Visuals**:\\r\\n  - Enhanced lighting system to improve realism and match the original Twilight Princess aesthetic.\\r\\n  - Updated texture resolution for character models, environment assets, and UI elements.\\r\\n  - Added post-processing effects, including bloom and ambient occlusion, for a polished visual experience.\\r\\n\\r\\n- **Gameplay Mechanics**:\\r\\n  - Improved combat system with smoother animations and hit detection.\\r\\n  - Recreated the original horseback riding mechanics for seamless player control.\\r\\n  - Enhanced enemy AI to make encounters more dynamic and challenging.\\r\\n\\r\\n- **Environment & World**:\\r\\n  - Fully remastered Ordon Village with updated geometry, textures, and lighting.\\r\\n  - Improved foliage interaction using Unity\'s Shader Graph for dynamic vegetation movement.\\r\\n  - Recreated Twilight Realm effects with custom shaders.\\r\\n\\r\\n- **Audio**:\\r\\n  - Remastered background music with high-quality samples inspired by the original soundtrack.\\r\\n  - Implemented 3D positional audio for immersive environmental effects.\\r\\n  - Added voiceover placeholders for key cutscenes.\\r\\n\\r\\n- **UI Improvements**:\\r\\n  - Redesigned HUD to better match modern resolutions while retaining the original feel.\\r\\n  - Added scalable elements for better support across multiple screen sizes.\\r\\n\\r\\n- **Other Features**:\\r\\n  - Initial implementation of a save/load system for player progress.\\r\\n  - Added a debug menu for internal testing and troubleshooting.\\r\\n  - Optimized game performance for stable framerate across mid-tier hardware.\\r\\n\\r\\n---\\r\\n\\r\\n## **Planned Features**\\r\\n- Implementing the Wolf Link transformation mechanics, including new animations and unique abilities.\\r\\n- Adding side quests and collectibles inspired by the original game.\\r\\n- Refining cutscenes with dynamic camera angles and character interactions.\\r\\n- Introducing a photo mode to capture the remastered visuals.\\r\\n- Exploring multiplayer or co-op functionality for certain segments, depending on demand.\\r\\n\\r\\n---\\r\\n\\r\\n## **Notes**\\r\\n- **Platforms**: Targeting PC (Windows) as the primary platform, with potential future expansion to mobile devices.\\r\\n- **Release**: No fixed release date yet; the project remains in active development.\\r\\n\\r\\n---\\r\\n\\r\\nThank you for your support as we continue to work on this passion project! Stay tuned for more updates."}]}')}}]);